 ---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Footer from "../components/footer.astro";
import Header from "../components/header.astro";
import PopUp from "../components/CTA PopUp.astro"
---
<Layout pageTitle="Free Resources">
  <Header />
  <section id="lead-magnet" class="page-section">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-xl p-8 md:p-12">
      
    <header style="text-align: center; padding: 40px 0 20px 0;">
      <h1 style="color: #1a365d; font-size: 2.5em; margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 1.2;">Protect Your Small Business—Before the Unexpected Hits</h1>
      <h3 style="color: #4a5568; font-weight: normal; font-size: 1.25em; max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto 30px auto; line-height: 1.5;">Grab your free Emergency Checklist and SEQ Risk Management Toolkit to keep your team, your assets, and your hard work safe.</h3>
    </header>

    <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 40px 0;">


      <p style="font-size: 1.1em; margin-bottom: 20px;">Running a small business in South East Queensland is incredibly rewarding. But between unpredictable severe weather, sudden operational disruptions, and the daily grind, risks are simply part of the landscape.
      When an emergency strikes, searching for policy numbers or scrambling for staff contact details shouldn't be what holds you up. <strong>Preparation isn't about expecting the worst—it’s about giving yourself total peace of mind so you can focus on what you do best.</strong>
      At Rivet Risk Services, we’re passionate about helping your small businesses stay resilient. That’s why we’ve built a straightforward, practical toolkit tailored specifically for our SEQ community.</p>

    <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 40px 0;">

      <h2 style="color: #1a365d; font-size: 1.8em; margin-bottom: 20px;">What’s Inside the Free Resilience Toolkit?</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1em; margin-bottom: 20px;">We’ve stripped away the complex corporate jargon to give you actionable, easy-to-use tools you can implement today.</p>
      
      <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; font-size: 1.05em;">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 15px;"><strong style="color: #1a365d;">The Master Emergency Checklist:</strong> A clean, printable template to house your most critical data. Keep your staff emergency contacts, insurance policy numbers, broker details, and utility accounts in one accessible place.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 15px;"><strong style="color: #1a365d;">SEQ Risk Management Resource Guide:</strong> A curated collection of free local tools, weather alert links, and risk-mitigation strategies designed specifically for the unique challenges of doing business in South East Queensland.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <blockquote style="background-color: #f7fafc; border-left: 4px solid #0073e6; margin: 0 0 30px 0; padding: 20px; font-style: italic; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;">
        <strong style="color: #1a365d; font-style: normal; display: block; margin-bottom: 5px;">Why download this today?</strong> In a crisis, every second counts. Having your critical numbers on a single sheet of paper can mean the difference between a minor hiccup 
        and a major financial loss. 
      </blockquote>
  

    <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 40px 0;">
    <div class="flex-container">
      <PopUp />
    </div>
    <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 40px 0;">
    <footer style="text-align: center; color: #718096; padding: 20px 0 40px 0;">
      <p style="font-weight: bold; color: #4a5568; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 1.1em;">Brought to you by Rivet Risk Services</p>
      <p style="font-style: italic; margin-top: 0;">We’re more than just risk specialists—we’re your neighbors. Let’s protect your hard work together.</p>
    </footer>
    </div>
  </section>
  <Footer /> 
</Layout> 